OL,3,CE-bike rider airlifted to hospital
OL,4,Cafter collision with van in Margate
OL,6,FThe rider of an e-bike has been
OL,7,Fairlifted to hospital in London with
OL,8,Fserious injuries following a collision
OL,9,Fwith a van in Margate.
OL,11,FThe accident happened on Northdown
OL,12,FRoad at around eleven o'clock this
OL,13,Fmorning.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the South East
OL,16,FCoast Ambulance Service has confirmed
OL,17,Fthat paramedics assessed and treated
OL,18,Fthe rider of the bike for injuries
OL,19,Fincluding to their head.
